### ============================================================
### Sales Orders
### Base URL: https://localhost:49609
###
### Full sales flow:
###   1. Checkout confirm    (presale.http)        → orderId
###   2. GET /api/orders/{id}                      → order details + paymentUrl (when Placed)
###   3. Web UI payment via  paymentUrl from step 2
###   4. POST /api/refunds   (refunds.http)        → request refund
### ============================================================

@baseUrl = https://localhost:49609
@token = YOUR_JWT_TOKEN
@contentType = application/json

# ============================================================
# AUTH
# ============================================================

### Login as admin
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/Login
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "email": "admin@localhost",
  "password": "aDminN@W25!"
}

###

# ============================================================
# ORDERS — own-scoped (admin/manager/service roles can view any)
# ============================================================

### Get order by id
# Expected: 200 OK  →  { id, number, cost, ordered, status, customerId, currencyId,
#                        couponUsedId, discountPercent, customer, orderItems,
#                        paymentUrl }  ← paymentUrl is non-null when status == "Placed"
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/orders/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
###

### Get order — not found
# Expected: 404 Not Found
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/orders/99999
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
###

### Get order belonging to another user (non-admin)
# Expected: 403 Forbidden
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/orders/2
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
###
